For a compressor of the kind shown in Fig. 1 the followings points lead to outage times, which are longer than needed:
● Repairing of appearing rubbing marks of the running blades at the inner wall of the housing 11' is hardly possible or difficult to achieve;
● For a potential compressor upgrade (larger annulus, etc.) the whole compressor housing 11' needs to be reworked or replaced.
